content:
Setup for Bring Your Own Channel is simple. Download a managed package from the App Exchange, create an Omni-Channel Flow for routing, and then install the Bring Your Own Channel messaging channel through a setup flow.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience

Prepare Your Agents to Use Bring Your Own Channel
Give agents the Service Cloud User license and prepare the agent console for Bring Your Own Channel.

Prepare Your Salesforce Org for Bring Your Own Channel
Before you set up Bring Your Own Channel, enable Omni-Channel, create a flow, and customize the agent console.

Create a Bring Your Own Channel Messaging Channel
To create a Bring Your Own Channel (BYOC) messaging channel, follow the setup flow.
title: Setting Up Bring Your Own Channel in Service Cloud
